みんなから愛されて
are loved by everyone.

296
00:30:16,869 --> 00:30:20,569
いいや 僕は
But that's fine, I...

297
00:30:20,569 --> 00:30:24,069
ずっと一人きりさ
will always be on my own.

298
00:30:24,469 --> 00:30:28,069
君と集まって星座になれたら
If I could be together with you and become a constellation,

299
00:30:28,069 --> 00:30:32,069
星降る夜 一瞬の願い事
A fleeting wish in that starry night...

300
00:30:32,469 --> 00:30:35,869
きらめいて ゆらめいて
Twinkling, shimmering,

301
00:30:35,869 --> 00:30:39,569
震えてるシグナル
quivering with light.

302
00:30:40,069 --> 00:30:43,769
君と集まって星座になれたら
If I could be together with you and become a constellation,

303
00:30:43,769 --> 00:30:47,869
