何億光年 離れたところには
Hundreds of millions of light years away,

309
00:31:14,669 --> 00:31:20,569
もう何かを知らない
we might already not know what's there anymore.

310
00:31:21,069 --> 00:31:24,569
月が綺麗で
Under the beautiful moon,

311
00:31:24,569 --> 00:31:28,569
