331
00:33:07,669 --> 00:33:11,269
つないだ線 解かないよ
I won't break the line that binds us together,

332
00:33:11,269 --> 00:33:16,869
君がどんなに眩しくても
No matter how dazzling you are.

333
00:33:32,369 --> 00:33:35,069
